graph TD
    classDef user fill:#6366f1,stroke:#4f46e5,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef planner fill:#0ea5e9,stroke:#0284c7,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef human fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,font-weight:bold,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    classDef specialist fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef synth fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef db fill:#f1f5f9,stroke:#cbd5e1,stroke-width:2px,color:#334155
    
    User[👩‍🔬 Scientist] -->|1. Enters complex research question| Planner
    
    subgraph The Planning Phase
        Planner[🧠 The Planner AI<br/>Breaks question into specific measurable tasks]
    end
    
    Planner -->|2. Drafts Research Protocol| Review[⏸️ Human Checkpoint<br/>Scientist reviews & approves the plan]
    
    subgraph The Execution Phase
        direction TB
        Review -->|3. Approved! Start tasks| Exec[⚙️ Execution Engine]
        
        Exec --> Spec1[🧬 Disease Specialist AI<br/>Analyzes genetic & drug data]
        Exec --> Spec2[🔬 Network Specialist AI<br/>Finds rising researchers]
        Exec --> Spec3[📄 Literature Specialist AI<br/>Extracts clinical evidence]
        
        Spec1 -.- OTD[(Open Targets database)]
        Spec2 -.- OA[(OpenAlex database)]
        Spec3 -.- PM[(PubMed database)]
        
        %% Chaining
        Spec1 -->|Passes target list to| Spec2
        Spec2 -->|Passes author names to| Spec3
    end
    
    subgraph The Synthesis Phase
        Spec1 & Spec2 & Spec3 -->|4. Unstructured insights| Synth[📝 The Synthesizer AI<br/>Writes final report]
        Synth -.- Grounding[🛡️ Google Search Grounding<br/>Fact-checks claims to prevent hallucinations]
    end
    
    Synth -->|5. Final Output| Brief[📄 Research Brief<br/>Fully cited, downloaded as PDF]
    
    class User user
    class Planner planner
    class Review,Grounding human
    class Spec1,Spec2,Spec3 specialist
    class Synth synth
    class OTD,OA,PM db
